00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,820
 spasitelja Isusa.

489
00:22:21,820 --> 00:22:23,300
 Tako će vam se

490
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:24,200
 pružiti sve

491
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,420
 što vam je potrebno.

492
00:22:25,420 --> 00:22:28,340
 Danas je blagdan

493
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:29,320
 srca Isusova

494
00:22:29,320 --> 00:22:30,920
 kojeg ova zajednica

495
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:32,240
 na poseban način časti

496
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,460
 i osobno ga časti.

497
00:22:33,460 --> 00:22:36,560
 Pazite šta se nudi

498
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:37,420
 koja su objećanja

499
00:22:37,420 --> 00:22:37,960
 onima koji će

500
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,140
 svakodnevno častiti

501
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:40,400
 srce Isusovo.

502
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,960
 Odnosno slijediti

503
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:43,740
 onoga

504
00:22:43,740 --> 00:22:44,760
 koji je dao život

505
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:45,260
 za tebe.

506
00:22:45,260 --> 00:22:47,220
 Daću im

507
00:22:47,220 --> 00:22:48,180
 sve milosti

508
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:49,280
 koje su im potrebne

509
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:52,040
 u njihovu staležu.

510
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:54,420
 Unijeću mir

511
00:22:54,420 --> 00:22:55,400
 u njihove obitelji.

512
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,240
 Tješit ću ih

513
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:57,460
 u svim njihovim patnjama.

514
00:22:57,460 --> 00:22:58,740
 Biću im sigurno

515
00:22:58,740 --> 00:22:59,840
 utočište za života

516
00:22:59,840 --> 00:23:01,260
 osobito na času smrti.

517
00:23:01,260 --> 00:23:02,700
 Izliću obilje

518
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:03,300
 blagoslova

519
00:23:03,300 --> 00:23:04,460
 na sve njihove pothvate.

520
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:06,220
 Griješnici će naći

521
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:06,880
 u mom srcu

522
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:07,760
 izvor i beskreno

523
00:23:07,760 --> 00:23:08,660
 more milosrđa.

524
00:23:08,660 --> 00:23:10,060
 Mlake će duše

525
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:10,940
 postati revne.

526
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,100
 Revne će duše

527
00:23:12,100 --> 00:23:12,600
 uzdići,

528
00:23:12,600 --> 00:23:13,660
 će se uzdići

529
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:15,380
 do velike savršenosti.

530
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:16,760
 Blagosloviću

531
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:17,580
 i kuće gdje bude

532
00:23:17,580 --> 00:23:18,560
 izložena i čašćena

533
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:18,920
 slika

534
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:19,960
 mog presjetog srca.

535
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:22,060
 Svećenicima

536
00:23:22,060 --> 00:23:22,960
 ću dati dar

537
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,100
 da taknu

538
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:24,700
 i najtvrdog

539
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:25,920
 kornija srca.

540
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,360
 Imena oni

541
00:23:27,360 --> 00:23:28,180
 koji budu širili

542
00:23:28,180 --> 00:23:28,940
 ovu pobožnost

543
00:23:28,940 --> 00:23:30,100
 bit će upisana

544
00:23:30,100 --> 00:23:30,720
 u mom srcu

545
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:31,800
 i neće se nikad

546
00:23:31,800 --> 00:23:32,440
 izbrisati.

547
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:34,280
 I ona zadnja

548
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:35,320
 svi koji se pričeste

549
00:23:35,320 --> 00:23:36,180
 na prve petke

550
00:23:36,180 --> 00:23:37,180
 neće ostati

551
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:37,960
 bez sakramenta

552
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:38,400
 ispovjedi

553
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,480
 pred svoju smrt.

554
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:41,920
 Sve je tu sadržano.

555
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:43,760
 Sve milosti.

556
00:23:43,760 --> 00:23:46,120
 A mi smo nestrpljivi.

557
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:47,840
 I ne puštamo

558
00:23:47,840 --> 00:23:49,280
 da nas Bog transformira

559
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:51,800
 nego idemo

560
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:52,800
 ispred njega.

561
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:57,100
 Zašto je do toga došlo?

562
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:58,780
 I kako?

563
00:23:58,940 --> 00:24:01,260
 Papa Franjo

564
00:24:01,260 --> 00:24:02,060
 jako dobro

565
00:24:02,060 --> 00:24:02,800
 to objašnjava.

566
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:05,900
 On govori

567
00:24:05,900 --> 00:24:07,040
 da se nalazimo

568
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:08,000
 u društvu

569
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:12,020
 koje je iskorjenjeno.

570
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,400
 Koje nema korjene.

571
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:15,540
 I o tome piše ovako.

572
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:17,180
 Čovjeku je strašno

573
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:18,260
 otuđenje osjećaj

574
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:19,480
 da nema korjena.

575
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:20,740
 To je da nikom ne pripada.

576
00:24:20,740 --> 00:24:22,500
 To su naši strahovi.

577
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:24,220
 Da nikom ne pripadaš.

578
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:26,280
 Najdublji.

579
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:28,600
 Da nemaš svoje mjesto.

580
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:29,780
 pa čak i ovdje u zajednici.

581
00:24:29,780 --> 00:24:30,900
 Znam da se mnogi borite

582
00:24:30,900 --> 00:24:31,260
 s tim.

583
00:24:31,260 --> 00:24:33,640
 Da ne vidiš

584
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,960
 gdje trebaš biti.

585
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:39,680
 Nema gore god osjećaja

586
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:41,100
 da si kod kuće stranac.

587
00:24:41,100 --> 00:24:42,240
 I to se dogodilo

588
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,220
 u našim obiteljima.

589
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:44,720
 To su obitelji

590
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:45,540
 bez povijesti,

591
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:48,060
 bez razgovora,

592
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:49,660
 bez intimnog odnosa.

593
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:50,200
 djeca.

594
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:52,380
 A djeca su ostavljena

595
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,380
 na milost i nemilost svijetu.

596
00:24:54,380 --> 00:24:56,600
 Da se sami snalaze.

597
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:59,120
 Sa osjećajima nepripadnosti

598
00:24:59,120 --> 00:25:00,200
 i

599
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:02,400
 strahom od nevoljenosti.

600
00:25:04,900 --> 00:25:06,160
 To je pozadina.

601
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:11,420
 I papa Franjo daje rješenje.

602
00:25:11,420 --> 00:25:15,600
 Kad ga je pitao taj novinar

603
00:25:15,600 --> 00:25:17,380
 čega se boju u životu,

604
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,340
 kad je bio mlad,

605
00:25:18,340 --> 00:25:18,860
 on je rekao,

606
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:20,720
 kao mlad silno sam se bojao.

607
00:25:20,720 --> 00:25:22,000
 Bojao sam se

608
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,160
 da me se ne voli.

609
00:25:24,140 --> 00:25:24,960
 I onda ga je pitao

610
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:26,600
 kak si to prevladao?

611
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:27,440
 Ipak je papa.

612
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:29,540
 I on je napisao

613
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:32,440
 Mislim da sam ga prevladao

614
00:25:32,440 --> 00:25:35,580
 tražeći autentičnost.

615
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:37,980
 Primijetio sam da nikada

616
00:25:37,980 --> 00:25:39,280
 ne bih napravio ništa

617
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:41,060
 što nije bilo autentično.

618
00:25:41,060 --> 00:25:43,420
 Pa nikako bi kupio ljubav

619
00:25:43,420 --> 00:25:44,760
 i poštovanje bližnjega.

620
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,180
 I ja sam se borio

621
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:47,340
 protiv društva privida,

622
00:25:47,340 --> 00:25:48,900
 društva u kojem je važan izgled,

623
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:50,440
 a to i dalje radim

624
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:52,760
 zadovoljavajući se time što jesam.

625
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:54,840
 Ali razmišljajući o slici

626
00:25:54,840 --> 00:25:56,980
 na kojoj još i danas često mislim.

627
00:25:56,980 --> 00:26:00,040
 I onda je dao sliku pauna.

628
00:26:00,040 --> 00:26:03,580
 I rekao da tako izgleda taština

629
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:04,380
 koju svijet nudi.

630
00:26:04,380 --> 00:26:05,620
 Zamislite pauna.

631
00:26:05,620 --> 00:26:06,780
 I kad raširi svoja

632
00:26:06,780 --> 00:26:09,040
 pera,

633
00:26:09,040 --> 00:26:09,820
 da šta već.

634
00:26:09,820 --> 00:26:11,260
 Da.

635
00:26:11,260 --> 00:26:13,300
 Predivan,

636
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:14,340
 veličanstven.

637
00:26:14,340 --> 00:26:16,200
 A onda papa Franju kaže

638
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,120
 ali to nije istina.

639
00:26:17,120 --> 00:26:19,660
 Morate ga dobro pogledat.

640
00:26:19,660 --> 00:26:21,220
 Morate ga obići.

641
00:26:21,220 --> 00:26:23,040
 I onda ga pogledaj

642
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,260
 da taština uvijek ima

643
00:26:24,260 --> 00:26:24,940
 i drugu stranu

644
00:26:24,940 --> 00:26:25,360
 i kaže,

645
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:26,920
 jeste ikad bili iza pauna?

646
00:26:26,920 --> 00:26:28,860
 Kakav je neugledan

647
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:30,240
 kad mu vidite stražnicu.

648
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:33,200
 To je taština

649
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:33,980
 koju svijet nudi.

650
00:26:33,980 --> 00:26:36,880
 I zato mi moramo biti autentični.

651
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:39,080
 Nema veće autentičnosti

652
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:39,980
 od svetosti,

653
00:26:39,980 --> 00:26:41,200
 na koju smo svi pozvani.

654
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,660
 I plodovi

655
00:26:42,660 --> 00:26:44,060
 ovoga bit će ono

656
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:45,060
 za čim čeznemo.

657
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,560
 naći će prijatelja

658
00:26:46,560 --> 00:26:48,800
 i naći će ženu

659
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:49,720
 ili muža.

660
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:58,160
 Prešao bi na

661
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:59,500
 taj poziv na odnos.

662
00:26:59,500 --> 00:27:01,140
 Na revoluciju

663
00:27:01,140 --> 00:27:02,240
 koju je Isus donio.

664
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:04,440
 Gledao sam,

665
00:27:05,900 --> 00:27:08,680
 vidio sam jedno istraživanje

666
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,260
 koje je

667
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:11,160
 jedno od rijetkih

668
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:11,760
 koje uspije

669
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:14,840
 da se tako provodi

670
00:27:14,840 --> 00:27:16,480
 kroz 75 godina.

671
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:17,960
 Se je provodilo jedno

672
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:18,720
 istraživanje

673
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,400
 na Harvardu.

674
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,700
 Oni su htjeli

675
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:23,080
 otkriti uzrok

676
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:23,700
 sreće

677
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:24,440
 izravlja

678
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:25,340
 ko čovjeka.

679
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:26,780
 Šta su radili?

680
00:27:26,780 --> 00:27:28,540
 Uzeli su studente,

681
00:27:28,540 --> 00:27:29,680
 njih 700 i nešto,

682
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:30,740
 sreće godine

683
00:27:30,740 --> 00:27:32,160
 i počeli ih

684
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:32,980
 intervjuirati.

685
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:34,740
 Svake godine

686
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,460
 su to radili.

687
00:27:35,460 --> 00:27:36,500
 Ali da

688
00:27:36,500 --> 00:27:38,040
 bude pošteno,

689
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:38,880
 uzeli su dio

690
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,220
 iz siromašne četvrti.

691
00:27:40,220 --> 00:27:41,600
 Najzabačenije.

692
00:27:41,600 --> 00:27:43,320
 I onda su ih

693
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:45,700
 intervjuirali

694
00:27:45,700 --> 00:27:46,580
 svake godine

695
00:27:46,580 --> 00:27:48,240
 o zdravlju,

696
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,940
 radili preglede,

697
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:50,840
 o

698
00:27:50,840 --> 00:27:52,620
 načinu života,

699
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:53,760
 o odnosima,

700
00:27:53,760 --> 00:27:54,640
 o jesu li

701
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:56,040
 ušli u obitelj.

702
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:58,020
 Tad su išli u rat,

703
00:27:58,020 --> 00:27:59,740
 pa su pričali o ratu,

704
00:27:59,740 --> 00:28:00,520
 pa su pričali

705
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:01,100
 o događajima

706
00:28:01,100 --> 00:28:02,000
 koji su proživjeli,

707
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:02,960
 pa su pričali

708
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:03,840
 o prijateljstvima,

709
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:05,260
 pa su pričali

710
00:28:05,260 --> 00:28:06,500
 o poslovima,

711
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:07,740
 pa su vidjeli

712
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:08,300
 da su neki

713
00:28:08,300 --> 00:28:09,000
 bili bogati

714
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:09,960
 i poslje siromašni,

715
00:28:09,960 --> 00:28:10,820
 neki siromašni

716
00:28:10,820 --> 00:28:11,520
 da su se uspjeli

717
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:12,700
 na toj ljestvici

718
00:28:12,700 --> 00:28:13,300
 bogatstva

719
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:14,100
 koji svijet nudi.

720
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:15,540
 Jedan od njih je čak

721
00:28:15,540 --> 00:28:16,320
 bio predsjednik,

722
00:28:16,320 --> 00:28:17,140
 pa je bilo oni

723
00:28:17,140 --> 00:28:17,720
 koji su bili

724
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:18,640
 psihički bolestni,

725
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:19,840
 neki su se čak i ubili.

726
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:22,940
 Bili oni

727
00:28:22,940 --> 00:28:24,560
 koji su se razveli

728
00:28:24,560 --> 00:28:25,100
 puno puta,

729
00:28:25,100 --> 00:28:25,940
 bili oni koji su imali

730
00:28:25,940 --> 00:28:26,860
 velike obitelji.

731
00:28:26,860 --> 00:28:29,820
 Tražeći

732
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:31,080
 sreći

733
00:28:31,080 --> 00:28:32,940
 i zdravlju,

734
00:28:32,940 --> 00:28:33,840
 došle su samo

735
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:34,240
 do jednog

736
00:28:34,240 --> 00:28:35,580
 zaključka

737
00:28:35,580 --> 00:28:36,960
 u 75 godina.

738
00:28:36,960 --> 00:28:38,940
 One osobe

739
00:28:38,940 --> 00:28:40,460
 koji su svoje vrijeme,

740
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:42,020
 trud,

741
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:43,060
 pa čak i novac,

742
00:28:43,060 --> 00:28:43,780
 ulagale

743
00:28:43,780 --> 00:28:45,280
 u zdrave

744
00:28:45,280 --> 00:28:46,320
 i čvrste odnose

745
00:28:46,320 --> 00:28:48,540
 sa prijateljima,

746
00:28:48,540 --> 00:28:49,740
 s djevojkom,

747
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:51,940
 sa zajednicom

748
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:53,140
 koji ih okružuje,

749
00:28:53,140 --> 00:28:54,780
 ti su imali

750
00:28:54,780 --> 00:28:55,620
 duži život,

751
00:28:55,620 --> 00:28:57,840
 sretniji

752
00:28:57,840 --> 00:29:00,040
 i bili su zdraviji.

753
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:05,580
 Ja sam to povezao

754
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:06,340
 sa revolucijom

755
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:07,160
 koju Isus donio.

756
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:11,820
 Isus nodi slobodu,

757
00:29:11,820 --> 00:29:14,020
 onu pravu istinsku.

758
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:17,700
 on je bio jedan od najvećih

759
00:29:17,700 --> 00:29:18,480
 liberala tad.

760
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:20,840
 Prekršio je sve norme

761
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:21,700
 i regule

762
00:29:21,700 --> 00:29:25,140
 koje su predsi mu

763
00:29:25,140 --> 00:29:25,660
 ostavili.

764
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:27,320
 Zbog čega?

765
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:30,280
 zbog drugoga,

766
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:31,220
 zbog bližnjega.

767
00:29:31,220 --> 00:29:32,500
 Pa je tad išo

