 Mi smo gotovi bili.

1308
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:38,420
 suze, jer ona je.

1309
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,100
 Ne zna šta bi od sebe.

1310
00:44:40,100 --> 00:44:42,620
 E to je mistika.

1311
00:44:42,620 --> 00:44:45,300
 Ko nas Bog želi pozvati.

1312
00:44:45,300 --> 00:44:49,040
 A Papa Franjo kaže jednu stvar

1313
00:44:49,040 --> 00:44:49,920
 ne smijemo izgubiti.

1314
00:44:54,620 --> 00:44:55,520
 posebno mi mladi.

1315
00:44:55,520 --> 00:44:57,640
 Ne smijemo izgubiti,

1316
00:44:57,640 --> 00:44:59,420
 kao kaže Papa Franjo,

1317
00:44:59,420 --> 00:45:08,000
 oduševljenost i radost.

1318
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,060
 i to mena dodaje smisla za humor.

1319
00:45:13,500 --> 00:45:14,500
 To nama treba.

1320
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:14,800
 To nama treba.

1321
00:45:14,800 --> 00:45:19,380
 Tad naše nošenje križa je podnošljivo.

1322
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:22,540
 Tad imamo perspektivu.

1323
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:24,180
 Tad nam Bog otvara.

1324
00:45:24,180 --> 00:45:25,760
 Ko što otvara ovoj zajednici.

1325
00:45:25,760 --> 00:45:27,220
 I vjerujem da će otvarati,

1326
00:45:27,220 --> 00:45:28,060
 tako se odazovemo.

1327
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:30,020
 i zato vas pozivam ovo ljeto.

1328
00:45:30,020 --> 00:45:32,580
 Odazovite se ovim pozivima.

1329
00:45:32,580 --> 00:45:34,760
 Pripremite svoje srce,

1330
00:45:34,760 --> 00:45:37,360
 jer Bog želi s vama nešto učiniti.

1331
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:40,540
 Želi vas podignuti stepenicu iznad.

1332
00:45:40,540 --> 00:45:42,840
 Želi vam dati možda službu,

1333
00:45:42,840 --> 00:45:44,940
 možda neki novi odnos prijateljstva.

1334
00:45:44,940 --> 00:45:47,700
 Koliko se toga samo u ovoj godini dogodilo.

1335
00:45:47,700 --> 00:45:49,660
 Imamo bebače.

1336
00:45:49,660 --> 00:45:52,980
 Imamo nove bračne parove.

1337
00:45:52,980 --> 00:45:54,860
 I zaručnike.

1338
00:45:58,360 --> 00:46:00,220
 Bog će davati.

1339
00:46:00,220 --> 00:46:02,020
 I ne moramo se bojati.

1340
00:46:02,020 --> 00:46:04,100
 On ima plan.

1341
00:46:04,100 --> 00:46:06,740
 A mi ostanimo radosni i u nadi.

1342
00:46:06,740 --> 00:46:09,240
 Kaže Papa Franjom da 40 godina

1343
00:46:09,240 --> 00:46:11,800
 moli ovu molitvu koja je meni jako dobra bila.

1344
00:46:11,800 --> 00:46:13,940
 I sad ću vam pročitati.

1345
00:46:13,940 --> 00:46:15,800
 To je napisao Thomas More

1346
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:20,200
 koji imao vrlo mnogo smisla za humor.

1347
00:46:20,200 --> 00:46:21,400
 On napisao ovako.

1348
00:46:21,400 --> 00:46:23,920
 Daj mi gospodine dobru probavu,

1349
00:46:23,920 --> 00:46:26,240
 a i nešto za probavljanje.

1350
00:46:27,240 --> 00:46:28,480
 Daj mi tjelesno zdravlje

1351
00:46:28,480 --> 00:46:31,100
 s dobrim raspoloženjem potrebnim da ga čuvam.

1352
00:46:31,100 --> 00:46:33,600
 Daj mi gospodine svetu dušu

1353
00:46:33,600 --> 00:46:36,380
 koje će blago biti ono što je dobro i čisto,

1354
00:46:36,380 --> 00:46:38,260
 da se ne preplaši grijeha,

1355
00:46:38,260 --> 00:46:40,880
 nego nek u tvojoj prisutnosti nađe način

1356
00:46:40,880 --> 00:46:42,540
 da stvari ponovno dovede u red.

1357
00:46:42,540 --> 00:46:45,780
 Daj mi dušu koja ne zna za dosadu,

1358
00:46:45,780 --> 00:46:48,760
 mrmljanja, uzdisanja, ni jadikovke.

1359
00:46:48,760 --> 00:46:51,540
 I ne dopusti da se pretjerano mučim

1360
00:46:51,540 --> 00:46:54,760
 radi onog previše nametljivog što se zove ja.

1361
00:46:55,800 --> 00:46:57,980
 Daj mi gospodine smisao za humor,

1362
00:46:57,980 --> 00:47:00,620
 udjeli mi milost razumijevanja šale,

1363
00:47:00,620 --> 00:47:03,280
 da u životu upoznam malo radosti

1364
00:47:03,280 --> 00:47:04,940
 i da je podijelim s drugima.

1365
00:47:04,940 --> 00:47:06,540
 Tako neka bude.

1366
00:47:06,540 --> 00:47:07,860
 Amen.

